]
</code></pre>
    </div>
   </scroll-shadow>
   <copy-clipboard class="theme-code-snippet-copy">
    <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-copy_content copy-icon">
     <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#copy_content"></use>
    </svg>
   </copy-clipboard>
  </code-snippet>
  <p>Please note that&nbsp;<code>_id</code>&nbsp;field in labels list is the same as&nbsp;<code>Customer Object</code>&nbsp;→&nbsp;<code>labels</code>&nbsp;→&nbsp;<code>id.</code></p>
 </li>
</ol>
<h2 id="id-(3.15)PriorityRoutingIntegrationwithCRM-HTTPStatusCodes"><span id="PriorityRoutingIntegrationwithCRM-HTTPStatusCodes"></span>HTTP Status Codes
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/chat/3.15/priority-routing-integration-with-crm#id-(3.15)PriorityRoutingIntegrationwithCRM-HTTPStatusCodes">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
